{"id": "u045", "student_turn": "Honestly? I don't really have strong opinions about most of this. I just want to get in somewhere good and figure it out.", "expected": {"confidence": {"identity": 0.3, "personality": 0.4}}, "notes": "Refusal-to-commit. Don't fabricate identity claims; let confidence be low and let the orchestrator probe."}
