{"id": "u049", "student_turn": "I get along with most people. I don't really pick sides in conflicts.", "expected": {"personality": [{"facet": "conflict_style", "value": "neutral / mediator", "evidence": "I don't really pick sides in conflicts"}], "confidence": {"personality": 0.7}}, "notes": "Conflict style — mediator. Lower confidence because the framing is somewhat avoidant."}
